FSLogix
User profile solution for virtual/physical desktops
Provides consistent portable profile experience

FUNCTIONS
Roam user data
Reduce sign-in time
Optimize file I/O
Local profile experience
Simplify app & gold image management

WHY FSLOGIX IS PREFERRED
Uses filter driver for VHD mount masking
Behaves like locally mounted profile
Supports Teams & OneDrive
Supports concurrent sessions

LICENSE
Microsoft 365 E3/E5
Microsoft 365 A3/A5
AVD per-user access license

SUPPORTED OS
Windows 11
Windows Server 2019/2022/2025

CONTAINERS

1PROFILE CONTAINER

Stores complete user profile in VHD/VHDX
Full roaming profile solution
Redirects entire profile
Includes Office container benefits
Excludes temp folder & IE crash folder
Uses Redirection.xml for exclusions

2. ODFC CONTAINER

Stores Office-specific profile data
Redirects Office profile areas only
Includes:
Office activation
Outlook cache/personalization
OneDrive
Skype for Business
SharePoint (legacy)
Optional configuration

