PROFILE TYPE
0 → Normal
1 → Read/Write
2 → Read-only
3 → Try Read/Write else Read-only

VHD DISK COMPACTION
Runs during sign out
Reduces VHD size automatically
Enabled by default
Depends on DefragSvc

REQUIREMENTS
Dynamically expandable drive
Disk compaction enabled
Container >1GB

FSLOGIX CONNECTION FLOW
1.User logs into FSLogix machine
2.Agent checks config & VHD location
3.VHD attaches if permissions are correct
4.Profile appears as local profile
5.VHD detaches at logoff

