Easier configuration

FSLOGIX APPLICATION RULE SET
Rules to show/hide/redirect/customize registry, files, apps, printers
Created using FSLogix Rule Editor

TYPES OF RULES
1.Hiding Rule
Hides files/folders/registry/printers/fonts
2.Redirection Rule
Redirects specific data to profile container
3.Specify Value Rule
Sets registry values during sign in

IMPORTANT
Creates:
.frx file → Rule
.fxa file → Assignment
Files must exist on all VMs

OTHER IMPORTANT POINTS
No support for Entra ID cloud-only accounts
Rules assigned to users/groups/process/network/computer/env variables
Default Everyone group = Applies set to No
Rules applied top to bottom

